_sText:
Finaly this is the release version of de_overdrive
for resuming it's a 52 spawns defuse/bomb map.
with 2 bomb site.
it takes place in a cyberpunk environement (ref to monalisa overdrive from W Gibson)
i've try to make a near futur dark city ambiance as you can see on the screens 

Objectives
Counter-Terrorists: Prevent Terrorists
from bombing the 2 chemical reserves.
Team members must defuse any 
bombs that threaten those reserves.

Terrorists: The Terrorist carrying the
C4 must destroy one of the chemical reserve. 

Special thanks to Rikku2000 for skybox models ;)
to the =[BraKass]= team for testing
